{"tid":2119534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"休班警藍田德田邨墮樓亡　昨晚涉偷拍裙底被捕　","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:37:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"8a744cf21e435adaca2efbbd5af91de44a65bcc0","tid":2119534,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"一名男子今（22日）早8時許，被發現倒臥於德田邨德盛樓平台，懷疑由高處墮下，當場身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者是一名37歲休班警員，駐守警察總部，主要負責內勤工作，他昨晚涉嫌偷拍裙底被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事主昨（21日）晚9時許休班時，在藍田啟田商場扶手電梯懷疑偷拍裙底被當場揭發，警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌偷拍將他拘捕，至凌晨時分獲准保釋，惟事主今早8時許被發現在居住的德田邨德盛墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，墮樓警員本身患有肌肉疾病及早期柏金遜症，去年曾請2個月大假，疑受病患影響，近月情緒低落，同事得悉其墮樓均感婉惜。"},{"pid":"f94886ca6d49974815781958bbd8a4d0f7e0371a","tid":2119534,"uid":359747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"29f9bf9d2b04004b539167f8c33fedb9b45a72bc","tid":2119534,"uid":34305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"Sources?"},{"pid":"3807421d19581da1ed2c7ec2644310e7539d86f0","tid":2119534,"uid":189157,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">死得好<br />\n想問下佢啲屋企人<br />\n幾時全家一齊落去陪佢?</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4de3567083bb032c5d05502c8551125d527da9","tid":2119534,"uid":202137,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"渣架，講聲自己人拉埋條女一邊屌都無人理啦"},{"pid":"130fc998da0bad19e7886918e5346ff9d705f7bc","tid":2119534,"uid":246020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b3d0e594fcd7e58e4d11d5b02fa4b2e81879dc","tid":2119534,"uid":224406,"like":2,